### Conflicts
Reviewers, this pull request conflicts with the following ones:

* #16377 ([rpc] don't automatically append inputs in walletcreatefundedpsbt by Sjors)

If you consider this pull request i
Please squash your commits according to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#squashing-commits
Sorry, thought I'd lost the suggestions from @MarcoFalke but they're all there after the squash. Thanks for those!
If you want the commit to be attributed to you, you might have to call `git commit --amend --author="Name <your@github.email>"`.\n\nOtherwise, this is good to merge now.

Or alternatively, add the mail that you used for the commit to your [github settings](https://github.com/settings/emails), this will make it link to you as well.\n\nLet's merge this immediately after the 0.20 feature freeze if we don't get response from the author.
Sorry, I didn't realise I had an old email address linked to my Github account. I've updated that now.
